Sandbox Banking (YC W17)| Software Engineers | Full-Time | Remote |<p>https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sandboxbanking.com&#x2F;careers&#x2F;
Sandbox provides Banking as a Service (BaaS) infrastructure for fintechs and banks. We help institutions quickly and securely integrate new software. We are growing quickly, YC backed, and possess an enviable runway. Our team is looking to hire exceptional individuals for the following:<p>Solution Delivery Engineer (https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sandboxbanking.com&#x2F;2021&#x2F;04&#x2F;30&#x2F;solution-delivery-software-engineer&#x2F;) Will scope requirements, develop, test and deploy specific customer integrations using our Glyue platform<p>Platform Software Engineer ( https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sandboxbanking.com&#x2F;2021&#x2F;04&#x2F;30&#x2F;platform-software-engineer&#x2F;) Will help build&#x2F;extend our core SaaS product (Glyue). Our stack is comprised of Vue&#x2F;JS&#x2F;HTML&#x2F;CSS, Python, Django, Postgres, Docker, Terraform, and an assortment of AWS services.<p>Senior Platform Software Engineer (https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sandboxbanking.com&#x2F;2021&#x2F;04&#x2F;30&#x2F;senior-platform-software-engineer&#x2F; ) Successful candidates will fulfill the requirements of our 
Platform Software Engineer role and also possess technical leadership, software architecture design, and devops abilities. A minimum of 4 years of professional experience is required.<p>Solution Delivery Network Engineer (https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sandboxbanking.com&#x2F;2021&#x2F;06&#x2F;11&#x2F;solution-delivery-infrastructure-engineer&#x2F;) Will be responsible for quickly delivering, managing, and monitoring the infrastructure and network resources necessary to delight our customers DevOps, aws, ec2, rds, route53, ansible, terraform, openvpn, ipsec experience helpful<p>Project Manager (https:&#x2F;&#x2F;sandboxbanking.com&#x2F;2021&#x2F;07&#x2F;30&#x2F;project-manager-remote&#x2F;) able to dive into the details of a specific integration while also thinking about the overall project time-line. They are able to manage customer expectations while holding internal and external stakeholders accountable for tasks required per a project plan
